Welcome to Lucky Pikas, the central command nexus of the Pika Power Universe.

You have arrived here for a reason. You are a Seeker, a Builder, an aspiring Commander in a world that encourages you to be a follower. You feel the pull of a higher purpose, a desire for a life of not just success, but of total sovereignty.

